Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.05,0:00:06.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:08.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,你鼻子都红了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:11.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,没办法啊  我都哭了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊果然是爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:17.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,你这人怎么这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,现在是说这个的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:21.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不会再让你哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:27.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不会再让你哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:32.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,你就好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:41.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:43.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,哇  是约定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:46.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:51.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽也和爸爸约好了  要永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:53.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,是吧  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:57.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,----op----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:11.87,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何なんだろう　この胸のモヤモヤは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:11.87,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}心中的这份躁动  是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:19.63,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}洗いたてのタオルに顔を埋めるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:19.63,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}就像将脸埋入刚洗过的毛巾一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:26.76,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥が鳴いている　朝焼けのメロディー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:26.76,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鸟儿们吟唱着  朝霞的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:37.82,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どこまで歩いても　この道は続いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:37.82,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}无论走到哪  这道路都会延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:46.92,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手を繋ぐよりも　指を繋ぐような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:46.92,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比起手牵手  更像是紧握这手指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:53.69,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒い夜は寄り添い合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:53.69,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒冷的夜晚彼此相依
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:59.05,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}星空の毛布で眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:59.05,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}以星空为毯子安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:04.29,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}テーブルの向こうの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:04.29,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}餐桌对面的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:12.73,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}最果ての地を君と目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:12.73,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}为你指向尽头之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:22.24,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}ありがとうはこっちの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:22.24,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我才该说谢谢你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:41.01,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1552.133,1062.267)}\N{\fade(1000,850)\blur6\pos(1502.133,1058.267)}向魔女寻求线索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:37.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:40.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,我说  你这都第几根甘蔗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,有留着大家的份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:47.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,好  剩下的没收
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  是索玛丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:51.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,啊  啊等下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:53.15,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,喂  都说住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:55.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,经过骆驼岩数个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:58.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们已经到了相当接近的地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:03.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  按这样前进的话估计明天就能穿越奥斯纳沙漠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:12.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,我是根据在沙漠的尽头看到过人类这一情报才来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过  看这个情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:22.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是在某处还有人类活着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,我说  乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么人类消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:47.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,不知道  战争或者其他的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,其他的理由是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么问这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,我什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,明明我也是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,明天也要早起  该睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,答应了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:17.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:19.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,我向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:33.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,身体的裂痕在日渐增大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:34.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,再这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:38.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,能打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,这次真的很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,多亏了你我才下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:53.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,直到最后一刻都一直和乌佐伊一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:58.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,我很久没有这样纯粹地想活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:05.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话  我也想一直守护到乌佐伊成人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:11.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,说实话我很羡慕你能见证索玛丽的成长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆每个个体都有固定的寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:26.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,我还有301天就会停止活动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,因此  我得在这副身体还能动的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,把索玛丽送到人类身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,这件事索玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,我没告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,我没有人类本身的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过我听说  穿过沙漠后再往西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,有个聚集了世间知识的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,去那里的话说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,世间的知识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:02.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,那就去那座村子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,不好意思  没能帮上多大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  现在无论多么微小的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,对我们来讲都是很大的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:13.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,我也旅行了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:22.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,带着人类小孩的旅行很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:28.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,确实  人类的小孩好奇心旺盛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,一移开视线马上就消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:34.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,又因为免疫力低下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,经常生病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:41.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,没有相关知识的看护  数次让我难以应付
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:46.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过这是为了索玛丽能健康成长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,也是些细小的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽很幸运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:59.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,这个世界已经没有人类的归宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:04.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,隐藏身份  被抓住的话不知道会被做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过  她遇到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:10.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,晚上能安心入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,能一直欢笑地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:20.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽能那样安心  一定是因为有你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,我也和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,担心能否守护索玛丽到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过  听了你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:36.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,有种这里稍微放松了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:37.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:42.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,这就是名为「安心」的感情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:45.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,哇  好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是到达沙漠尽头的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,和你们的旅行也快结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:04.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,昨天不是说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,我一直在吃都没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么要笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为很奇怪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:17.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,我还想和你们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:24.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,这不是什么伤心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,总有一天还会再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,在治好海特拉的病后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:39.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,说实话  我还不是全部都接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过现在我的感情也并非虚假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,一定  总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,你们两个  看得到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:58.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,是森林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,沿着这条河走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,应该就能到之前说的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:10.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  接下来要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,去可能能得到情报的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,去那里就能知道人类的事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:17.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,有这个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,太好了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:27.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,太好了呢  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,再见  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,再见  乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,是个相当奇特的村子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:13.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,你好  小小的旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,要不要来一杯魔女特制的威卡葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,小孩子也能放心喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:21.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,威卡葡萄酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,要不要一起来点红莓酱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,还有添加了香草的香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,还有彩色泡菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:32.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,魔女的村子好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:40.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽  我们可不是来这里吃饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:42.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,情报在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,难道你们在调查些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:48.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:55.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,那里就是聚集了世间知识的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,魔女印图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:58.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,我来带路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  好多书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,这确实超出了我的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:16.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,听说单是关于医学的书籍就超过了一万册
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:18.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,多年的困扰终于能够解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,这下能够有所期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:22.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸你快看  这是关于食物的书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,全世界的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,午后的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,还有肉食盛宴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.89,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,看起来都好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,你脑子里好像只有吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,久等了  旅人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,她叫海泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,图书馆里特别能干的管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,那么我先离开了  祝你们能够找到想要找的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,海泽尔  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:50.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:54.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,请问来到图书馆是有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们为寻找人类而踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,来到这里寻求线索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,线索是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:03.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:16.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,确实在藏书中有一本记载了人类传记的书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:17.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,传记？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:19.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽要读那本书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,那本书对你来说还很难哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,没事的  我会努力读的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽想要知道好多人类的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:32.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是奇怪的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,那么我来带路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:41.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们魔女是信仰这个世界的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,对创造了天地和孕育了生命的神明充满感激之情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,为了不忘记如此伟业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们自远古起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:51.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,就在全世界开始收集书籍并保管于这个图书馆中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,有离开村庄收集书籍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:14:00.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,也有像我们这样  将收集来的书籍进行管理的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,还有保护书籍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:08.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,这些都是从远古以前流传下来的魔女的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:12.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,也能够说是我们一族的本能  所以说没有任何报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:18.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以我们通过运用知识制成药品和制作食物来贩卖从而获得收入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,全部都很好吃哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,我会向大家传达的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:25.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:28.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,要找的书应该就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,让我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:34.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,奇怪  应该是在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,也没有借出的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,是丢失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:46.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是  我已经有头绪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:51.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是见笑了  图书馆里有时会出现书虫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,虫子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  根据我的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:57.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,大概  在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,普拉丽娜  你在这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,是海泽尔啊  你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:13.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,那就是书虫  我的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:14.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,你们好哇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:17.56,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,真是的  要说多少次…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆啊  为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:22.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,真的好大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:23.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,还好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个那个  你们从哪儿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:27.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:29.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,关于人类的书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:36.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,是挺久以前的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:39.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,我说你啊  普拉丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,对待书籍不要这么粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:44.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,我也来找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,那本书的名字是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:50.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,好像是叫海纳斯传记
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:16:02.05,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,海纳斯  海纳斯  海纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:51.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,装订的外表呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:54.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,特别的又老又破
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:55.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,太粗略了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:16:01.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,还有整体偏蓝  好像还有一只眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  书找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:09.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:12.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,我现在就拿过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:15.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,没事吧  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:37.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:41.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃书的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,骨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,喜欢吃墨水浸透的旧纸张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,是我们魔女的天敌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:53.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,繁殖期的时候倒是特别多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,还不是因为你的房间这么乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:01.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:06.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是数量好像还是很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,海泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:21.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:51.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,魔法好厉害  好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:56.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的使魔很强但是攻击范围比较小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是海泽尔的魔法攻击范围却很大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:03.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以我们两人组合起来就是天下无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,总是说些奉承话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,好像还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:29.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,好  好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:31.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,第一次见到那样的亚种
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:39.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,你这条大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:55.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,它在看着书
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,难道是盯上了海纳斯传记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽  暂且先把书放下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:10.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是很重要的书
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:14.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,情报…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:52.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,确认为敌人  立即排除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:24.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽完全没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:35.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是  爸爸才不是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,看上去好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,都怪索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,海泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,这本海纳斯传记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,已经无法阅读了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,我没有保护好书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:03.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:12.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,只要索玛丽没事  就没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想到了  如果能查找借阅表的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:34.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,说不定能够找到阅读过的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:35.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,确实可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:37.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,可行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:38.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:43.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,304年前  只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:48.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,是个图书馆管理人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:52.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,伊索尔德·内波夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:54.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,你说的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,对  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:02.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,是这座图书馆的馆长
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
